name: Plan Express
overview: Plan Express, Inc., a document management, printing, and logistics company, engages in the management, printing, reproduction, and distribution of construction documents, plans, and contract specifications. The company offers centralized print ordering that includes organizing project plans, scanning plans and documents, accepting digital uploads, and indexing and posting to a plan room; document management, such as online plan rooms, revision tracking, digital archiving, and document storage; distribution and logistics; and other services comprising color reproductions. It serves engineers, architects, owners, construction managers, and contractors. The company has strategic partnerships with Reed Construction Data, Onvia, and USGN. Plan Express, Inc. was founded in 1994 and is based in Memphis, Tennessee with additional offices in Phoenix, Arizona; and Chicago, Illinois. The company has hub print fulfillment centers in Chicago, Illinois; New York, New York; Philadelphia, Pennsylvania; Boston, Massachusetts; Dallas, Texas; Phoenix, Arizona; and San Mateo, California.
